{"tid":1417340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[救人][尋人] 8.3晚係黃大仙既同我入哂黎!!","createTime":"2019-08-05T16:24:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T14:37:10.000Z","uid":235931,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"88682de7aa177f678c15575604f4e9c213661dda","tid":1417340,"uid":235931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:24:26.000Z","msg":"有學生義士又比差佬格硬屈。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1414823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1414823</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\">頭先手快打錯日期 而家再開過！<br />\n</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WjVHdvv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWjVHdvv.png&h=d00ee0e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n尋日黑警已經開咗file charge咗佢話佢襲警 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係佢俾人埋身嗰時兩隻手舉撚高曬 但係咁啱影唔到嗰下<br />\n所以有冇人有片影到佢比人郁嗰下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫手推一推救救呢個學生...唔好比啲仆街黑警得逞。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">時間係大約2245-2300<br />\n已知有熱血公民fb live 但條片無佢比人岩岩捉個時姐係成件事個開頭<br />\n所以證據未夠幫到佢!!</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w3MSAJU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw3MSAJU.png&h=75a0313c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇番live發現應該有巴絲係附近錄片 如果有片做證既可以 <a href=\"http://t.me/tmismyhome\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftmismyhome&d=aRHHWgZm4a4JNL46Iov0BDH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=4849ef3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/tmismyhome</a> <br />\n<br />\n好人一生平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a6353b28dea7a968d589ea590835337a51dcb23","tid":1417340,"uid":235931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:24:42.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"3ccdac9af95c18abb04a8015ca52c47145c168fa","tid":1417340,"uid":235931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0